mage/20160108/1452256633.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/puti/uploads/image/20160108/1452256203.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/puti/uploads/image/20160108/1452257954.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/puti/uploads/image/20160108/1452254012.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/puti/uploads/image/20160108/1452252772.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>', '', '', 'uploads/image/20160108/1452255524.jpg', '', '13', '99', '1452249587', 'true', '', '0', '330', '0', '0', null, null, '0', '0', '0', '1000', '430');
INSERT INTO `lxlp_goods` VALUES ('14', '4', '0', '0,', '9', '4', '0,4,', '-1', '-1', '', '台湾东方美人茶', '', '', '', '', '', '东方美人茶', '1', '0.0', '0.00', '2000', '2000', '2000', '0.00', 'a:3:{i:1;s:4:\"5.00\";i:2;s:4:\"7.00\";i:3;s:5:\"10.00\";}', 'admin', '', '', '', '<p style=\"color:#666666;font-family:\'Microsoft Yahei\';white-space:normal;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#000000;\"> “奕昇缘”品牌是奕生缘企业秉承“天然、健康、绿色”的企业宗</span><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#000000;\">旨打造的品牌，旨在送一</span><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#000000;\">份</span><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#000000;\">安心给消费者，传承一份爱的福祉，</span><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#000000;\">坚持一份销售，一份绿色，一</span><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#000000;\">份健康。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#666666;white-space:normal;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"color:#6AA84F;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:kaiti_gb2312;\">【东方美人茶的特征】</span></strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#666666;white-space:normal;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#444444;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">茶叶会自然吐出类似农药的味道，因此无虫害问题，无需喷农药，更不需肥料。野生茶的茶叶都有小绿叶蝉咬食的痕迹，春季是它的产茶期，一年仅采摘一次。</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18px;color:#444444;line-height:1.5;\">台湾原生种茶树产于南横公路六龟、藤枝一带，以野生茶种为主，台湾每年产量过5000~6000斤，极其稀贵。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#666666;white-space:normal;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#444444;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#666666;white-space:normal;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#783F04;\"><span style=\"font-family:kaiti_gb2312;\">【它的功效】</span></span></strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#666666;white-space:normal;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"color:#444444;\">适合熬夜、饮酒的人群。若酒醉，可泡一壶野生茶，饮后约半小时，可醒酒。另外，人称熬夜的好朋友，长期熬夜的人可作为日常饮品饮用，可护肝养肝。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#666666;white-space:normal;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"color:#444444;\"><img src=\"/puti/uploads/image/20160108/1452260187.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></span></span> \r\n</p>', '', '', 'uploads/image/20160108/1452256240.jpg', '', '1', '100', '1452252172', 'true', '', '0', '0', '0', '0', null, null, '0', '0', '0', '1000', '200');
